THEM ED:------------------https://vn.elsaspeak.com/cach-them-duoi-ed/

co quy tac: go ahead
THDB:
	e cam hoac ee: them d

bat quy tac

	mot am tiet: 
		cuoi = hwyx: + ed bowed
		cuoi = nguyen_am + nguyen_am + phu_am + ed waited
		cuoi = phu_am + nguyen_am +phu_am -> phu_am^2 + ed knitted

	hai am tiet
		trong am -> am thu nhat
			khong nhan doi phu am: offered
		trong am -> am thu hai (am nhan trong am)
			nguyen_am + phu_am: phu_am^2 + ed preferred
			
	end = Y
		nguyen_am + y = yed deployed
		phu am + y = ied tried
PHAT AM ED:------------------
	t:
		/k/, /p/, /t/ /s/, /f/, /ʃ/, /tʃ/ 
		p, k, gh, s, sh, ch
	id:
		t hoac d
	d:
		cach truong hop con lai(end = am huu thanh, nguyen am ueoai..)
THDB:
	Naked, Scared, Blessed, Crabbed
	
